                    <h3>Jeannette R. Holtham</h3>
                    <p><strong>Author, President, and Founder of Youth Transformation Center</strong></p>
                    <p>Jeannette is a recognized leader in Colorado’s restorative justice movement, with extensive experience working with high-risk youth in alternative schools, detention centers, and prisons. She holds a BA in communications, graduating summa cum laude from Regis University. Her work has contributed significantly to advancing restorative justice in schools and the judicial system.</p>
